data.text: @WallsiesDGP yes! i had barely any symptoms. only slight pain in my arm and a headache. so the second has definitely hit me a harder.
@cursedrats Had my first on Monday and it’s knocked me for 6, was your symptoms to your first any different to your second?
my symptoms from afterwards if anyone is nervous about getting it and wants to know: so far, my arm is extremely sore from where i got it and i also have a 101.4 fever and chills.
